entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: Commander Talte had you chasing a wild durni. Jareck isn't involved.
entries.journal_entry_description: Find out whether Jareck is involved with these kidnappings.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: While Commander Talte is researching the items that you found, talk to the hermit, Jareck, and keep him busy.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: Angela didn't recognize any of the pieces. But, I found matches in the CorSec database and they are tied to several kidnappings. It's going to trial very soon and I need more information.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: You received a message from Talte: Angela didn't recognize any of the pieces. But, I found matches in the CorSec database and they are tied to several kidnappings. It's going to trial very soon and I need more information.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Talk to the hermit again and get his side of the story.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Jareck mentioned that he met with traders nearby. Go to the location that he mentioned.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Look around and see if there's something that matches Jareck's story.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: This art piece has both blood and fingerprints on it. The fingerprints on the art do not match the hermit's fingerprints.
entries.task05_message_box_text: This art piece has both blood and fingerprints on it. The fingerprints on the art do not match the hermit's fingerprints.
entries.task06_comm_message_text: I've had you chasing a dead lead. Another group of people disappeared. I'll send you the coordinates.  Go there now.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Commander Talte sent you a message: I've had you chasing a dead lead. Another group of people disappeared. I'll send you the coordinates.  Go there now.
